 sellers are cutting — most are pricing to the current market from day one.</p>\n\n<figure style=\"margin:2rem 0;background:#faf8f4;border:1px solid #e5dfd4;border-radius:8px;padding:1.5rem\">\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 90\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:500px;display:block;margin:0 auto\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Active Listings by Price Range\">\n    <text x=\"250\" y=\"18\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1a1918\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Cormorant Garamond,Georgia,serif\">Active Listings by Price Range</text>\n    <rect x=\"20\" y=\"32\" width=\"166\" height=\"28\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\"/><rect x=\"186\" y=\"32\" width=\"120\" height=\"28\" fill=\"#cda96f\" rx=\"0\"/><rect x=\"306\" y=\"32\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" fill=\"#d4b98a\" rx=\"0\"/><rect x=\"414\" y=\"32\" width=\"66\" height=\"28\" fill=\"#e0cca8\" rx=\"0\"/><text x=\"103\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">Under $400K</text><text x=\"246\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">$400K–$600K</text><text x=\"360\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">$600K–$1M</text><text x=\"447\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">Over $1M</text>\n  </svg>\n  <figcaption style=\"font-size:11px;color:#999690;text-align:center;margin-top:.5rem;font-family:Inter,sans-serif\">Source: Austin MLS Active Listings · April 13, 2026</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n<figure style=\"margin:2rem 0;background:#faf8f4;border:1px solid #e5dfd4;border-radius:8px;padding:1.5rem\">\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 319\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:500px;display:block;margin:0 auto\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Active Listings by Zip Code\">\n    <text x=\"250\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#