    "content": "\n<div style=\"position:relative;margin:2rem 0;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#0f0f0e\">\n  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:.7\"\n         src=\"/videos/hero-video.mp4\">\n  </video>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;text-align:center;padding:2rem\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b8935a;margin-bottom:.75rem\">Austin TX Real Estate</p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,4vw,2.5rem);color:#fff;line-height:1.25\">Austin Real Estate Neighborhood Spotlight — Week of March 26, 2026</p>\n  </div>\n</div><p>The Austin real estate market is really ten markets in one — central neighborhoods, east side, south Austin, the northern suburbs, the Hill Country fringe. This week's report for <strong>March 26, 2026</strong> breaks down the MLS data by zip code so you can see which areas have the most activity, the best values, and the most competition.</p><h2>Austin Real Estate by Zip Code — Week of March 26, 2026</h2>\n<div class=\"data-highlight\"><span class=\"stat\">500</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Total Metro Active Listings</span></div>\n<div class=\"data-highlight\"><span class=\"stat\">$490,000</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Metro Median Price</span></div>\n<div class=\"data-highlight\"><span class=\"stat\">0 days</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Metro Avg Days on Market</span></div>\n\n<figure style=\"margin:2rem 0;background:#faf8f4;border:1px solid #e5dfd4;border-radius:8px;padding:1.5rem\">\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 480 319\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:480px;display:block;margin:0 auto\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Active Listings by Zip Code (Top 6)\">\n    <text x=\"240\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1a1918\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Cormorant Garamond,Georgia,serif\" letter-spacing=\"0.02em\">Active Listings by Zip Code (Top 6)</text>\n    \n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">78641 · $594K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"40\" width=\"270\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"407\" y=\"62\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">18 homes</text>\n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"106\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">78660 · $452K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"84\" width=\"270\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"407\" y=\"106\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">18 homes</text>\n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">76537 · $330K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"128\" width=\"210\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"347\" y=\"150\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">14 homes</text>\n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"194\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">78620 · $1331K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"172\" width=\"210\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"347\" y=\"194\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">14 homes</text>\n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"238\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">78642 · $499K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"216\" width=\"210\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"347\" y=\"238\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">14 homes</text>\n    <text x=\"124\" y=\"282\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"12\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">78610 · $652K avg</text>\n    <rect x=\"130\" y=\"260\" width=\"180\" height=\"34\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.9\"/>\n    <text x=\"317\" y=\"282\" fill=\"#b8935a\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter,system-ui,sans-serif\">12 homes</text>\n  </svg>\n  <figcaption style=\"font-size:11px;color:#999690;text-align:center;margin-top:.5rem;font-family:Inter,sans-serif\">Source: Austin MLS Active Listings · March 26, 2026</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n<h2>Top Zip Codes This Week</h2>\n<h3>78641 — 18 Active Listings · Avg $594K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 18 active listings and an average price of $594,191, zip code 78641 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p><h3>78660 — 18 Active Listings · Avg $452K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 18 active listings and an average price of $452,363, zip code 78660 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p><h3>76537 — 14 Active Listings · Avg $330K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 14 active listings and an average price of $329,944, zip code 76537 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p><h3>78620 — 14 Active Listings · Avg $1331K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 14 active listings and an average price of $1,331,200, zip code 78620 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p><h3>78642 — 14 Active Listings · Avg $499K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 14 active listings and an average price of $499,384, zip code 78642 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p><h3>78610 — 12 Active Listings · Avg $652K · 0 avg DOM</h3>\n<p>With 12 active listings and an average price of $652,166, zip code 78610 is one of Austin's most active markets this week. Average days on market of 0 suggests strong buyer demand — homes here are moving quickly.</p>\n\n<figure style=\"margin:2rem 0;background:#faf8f4;border:1px solid #e5dfd4;border-radius:8px;padding:1.5rem\">\n  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 480 80\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:480px;display:block;margin:0 auto\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Austin Active Listings by Price Range\">\n    <text x=\"240\" y=\"18\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1a1918\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Cormorant Garamond,Georgia,serif\">Austin Active Listings by Price Range</text>\n    <rect x=\"20\" y=\"30\" width=\"164\" height=\"24\" fill=\"#b8935a\" rx=\"2\"/><rect x=\"184\" y=\"30\" width=\"92\" height=\"24\" fill=\"#cda96f\" rx=\"2\"/><rect x=\"276\" y=\"30\" width=\"105\" height=\"24\" fill=\"#d4b98a\" rx=\"2\"/><rect x=\"381\" y=\"30\" width=\"63\" height=\"24\" fill=\"#e5dfd4\" rx=\"2\"/><text x=\"102\" y=\"72\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">Under $400K</text><text x=\"230\" y=\"72\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">$400K–$600K</text><text x=\"328.5\" y=\"72\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">$600K–$1M</text><text x=\"412.5\" y=\"72\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5c5b57\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\">Over $1M</text>\n  </svg>\n  <figcaption style=\"font-size:11px;color:#999690;text-align:center;margin-top:.5rem;font-family:Inter,sans-serif\">Source: Austin MLS Active Listings · March 26, 2026</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n<h2>Reading the Zip Code Data</h2>\n<p>Zip code activity count (number of active listings) tells you about supply. Average days on market tells you about demand relative to that supply. A zip code with low listing count and low DOM is undersupplied — prices there tend to hold firm. A zip code with high listing count and high DOM is oversupplied — buyers have leverage. The most competitive situations are low inventory + low DOM = multiple offers.</p>\n<div style=\"margin:2.5rem 0;padding:2rem;background:#0f0f0e;border-radius:8px;text-align:center\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b8935a;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Work with Luke Allen · Austin TX Realtor</p>\n  <p style=\"font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.75rem\">Questions about the Austin market?</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:1.5rem;max-width:480px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\">Luke Allen is an Austin TX Realtor (TREC #788149) specializing in buyer and seller representation across all Austin zip codes. 15 five-star Google reviews.</p>\n  <a href=\"/about#contact\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#b8935a;color:#fff;padding:.8rem 2rem;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500\">Schedule a Free Consultation →</a>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:2rem 0;padding:1.5rem;background:#faf8f4;border:1px solid #e5dfd4;border-radius:8px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b8935a;margin-bottom:.75rem\">Related Resources</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem\">\n    <a href=\"/market-report\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#b8935a;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(184,147,90,.3);border-radius:100px;padding:.3rem .9rem\">Live Market Report</a>\n    <a href=\"/investment-properties\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#b8935a;text-decoration